Ren Ziwei of Team China won the gold medal in the short track speed skating men's 1000-meter final at the 2022 Winter Olympic Games at Capital Indoor Stadium in Beijing on Monday. Su Yiming of Team China won the silver medal in the men's snowboard slopestyle by scoring 88.70 points at Genting Snow Park in Zhangjiakou, north China's Hebei Province, on Monday. Gu Ailing of Team China reached the women's freeski big air final after competing in the qualification at Big Air Shougang in Beijing on Monday. Mikaela Shiffrin of the U.S. failed to finish the women's giant slalom Run 1 at the 2022 Winter Olympics at the National Alpine Skiing Center in Yanqing, Beijing, on Monday.